flowchart LR
  Plan[Plan: goals, scope, assumptions] --> Discover[Discover: research and evidence]
  Discover --> Explore[Explore: alternatives and sketches]
  Explore --> Define[Define: wireframes, IA, microcopy]
  Define --> Design[Design: visual system and prototype]
  Design --> Validate[Validate: test and measure]
  Validate --> Deliver[Deliver: handoff, QA, release]
  Validate -- iterate --> Define
  Deliver -- product feedback --> Plan
